## 🤖 About

KIND-TGPT is a sophisticated AI system that combines:
- **TGPT Integration** - Advanced language model capabilities
- **Memory System** - Persistent learning across sessions
- **Web Dashboard** - Beautiful user interface
- **REST API** - Easy integration
- **Self-Learning** - Improves over time

## 🚀 Quick Install

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Karlfiner-Robotiken/KIND-TGPT.git
cd KIND-TGPT

# Install
chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh

# Start the AI
kind-tgpt start
```

